title: how to make another's order visible in your notes
pid: 60c345f3-a5c5-4ffe-bd1d-204eb059286e
body: |2-
  For each node of yours and root that it contains-descends from,
  if the other author has a different path to it, indicate that they do.
  The same for your own -- if this node can be got to from the view-root
  (and generalizations thereof) in another way, something indicates that plurality.
